WEBVTT

00:06.753 --> 00:09.313
<i>In New York City's
war on crime,</i>

00:09.389 --> 00:11.414
<i>the worst criminal offenders
are pursued</i>

00:11.491 --> 00:14.324
<i>by the detectives
of the Major Case Squad.</i>

00:14.394 --> 00:16.361
<i>These are their stories.</i>

00:19.466 --> 00:21.593
Beeatch!
What's your problem?

00:21.668 --> 00:23.135
Mom, Gloria polished off all the milk.

00:23.203 --> 00:24.864
Did you take my soccer
uniform out of the dryer yet?

00:24.938 --> 00:27.133
Yes, I agree.
It's intolerable.

00:27.207 --> 00:28.572
Do we have any more milk? Yeah, hold on.

00:28.642 --> 00:31.475
Check the downstairs fridge.
Honey, it's in your closet.

00:31.545 --> 00:33.206
Has Sean come out
of his room yet?

00:33.280 --> 00:34.508
Uh-uh.
What's the drama?

00:34.581 --> 00:37.778
Oh! He wants to go to a party,
and the parents won't be home.

00:37.851 --> 00:38.840
Sorry, go on.

00:38.919 --> 00:40.477
Anyone see my belt?

00:40.554 --> 00:44.684
Yes, I will put it on my calendar
for this afternoon. Great, okay.

00:45.425 --> 00:47.416
Sean, sweetie,
come on, we gotta go!

00:47.494 --> 00:49.359
Don't call me sweetie.

00:55.369 --> 00:56.734
Let's go.

